Package com.cafean.JobStatus.ui.stream

Class JobStatusLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.jobstream.common.util.StreamLogger
      • com.cafean.JobStatus.ui.stream.JobStatusLogger
  • public class JobStatusLogger
extends StreamLogger
    A logging adapter used to provide error, warning, etc. message hooks for modules loaded by the client side (i.e. ModelEditor side) of the Job Stream system.
